Subject: [PATCH 025/518] t4240/dts: Add alias for "crypto" node.

This is required since u-boot searches for crypto node for adding
fsl,sec-era property.

Signed-off-by: Vakul Garg <vakul@freescale.com>
Signed-off-by: Andy Fleming <afleming@freescale.com>
[Grabbed from the branch, LINUX_IR5.2.0, of
https://git.freescale.com/git-private/cgit.cgi/ppc/alu-b4860/linux.git.]
Signed-off-by: Tiejun Chen <tiejun.chen@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-pre.dtsi |    1 +
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-pre.dtsi b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-pre.dtsi
index 001dbbe..77bbdb0 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-pre.dtsi
+++ b/arch/powerpc/boot/dts/fsl/t4240si-pre.dtsi
@@ -51,6 +51,7 @@
 		qman = &qman;
 		pme = &pme;
 		dce = &dce;
+		crypto = &crypto;
 		fman0 = &fman0;
 		fman1 = &fman1;
 		ethernet0 = &enet0;
